comments: Ayton (PHX) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Bridges (PHX) establishes himself in a legal guarding position while Morant (MEM) creates the contact during his shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) and Booker (PHX) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball.
Morant (MEM) reaches in and makes contact to Booker's (PHX) arm after he gathers the ball on his shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) turns and slightly extends his arm into Bridges (PHX) at the end of the pick.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Brooks (MEM) makes contact to Rubio's (PHX) arm during his shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) grabs Morant's (MEM) wrist as he splits the two defenders and the contact affects his ability to maintain control of the ball during the drive.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) and Morant (MEM) arrive at the ball simultaneously during the loose ball and the body contact that occurs when the two players come together is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Rubio (PHX) in transition.
Anderson (MEM) swipes down and makes hand on ball contact with Oubre Jr. (PHX) during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the on-court ruling was overturned to Grizzlies' ball.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes contact to Booker's (PHX) head.
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Oubre Jr. (PHX) jumps and does not extend his arm in an unnatural path during his shot attempt. All contact occurs after Anderson (MEM) moves under Oubre Jr. (PHX) during his natural shooting motion.
Bridges (PHX) commits a take foul on Anderson (MEM).
